{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Fickle_Crowd",
  "title": "A Fickle Crowd",
  "summary": "Outside the New Republic Embassy on the world of Caspar, a growing crowd of mostly Human and Sarian protesters gathers at dawn, brandishing populist placards demanding the Republic leave amid an Imperial blockade overhead. Ambassador Ambrosia emerges to address them, flanked by a Sarian aide and a protocol droid, and attempts to redirect their anger toward the Empire, arguing that the blockade and resource seizures are Imperial coercion rather than Republic provocation. Despite her amplified appeals to Caspian pride, independence, and the memory of past Imperial aggression, the crowd remains hostile and resumes its chant of 'New Republic out.' Unable to win them over, Ambrosia plants a colorful handmade sign reading 'CASPAR IS PROUD, KEEP HER FREE' on the embassy steps and retreats inside, leaving the restless protest behind.",
